description: LibriVox recording of The Green Forest Fairy Book by Loretta Ellen Brady. Read in English by Peter Yearsley; Claudia Salto; BettyB; John Kellow; Deefry; Sim; Sandra Knight; Joseph Tenis; James K. White; SamW. This is a volume of original fairy tales by Loretta Ellen Brady. - Summary by Carolin. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
